### 1. 先报修一个故障 (ID 假设生成为 2)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/issues/report
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "scooterId": 2,
  "description": "The headlight is broken.",
  "priority": "medium"
}

### 2. 管理员查看，发现有条新报修
GET http://localhost:8080/api/issues

### 3. 管理员处理这条报修
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/issues/resolve/2